name: Dbws
tagline: Software update DBWS. Program for rietveld analysis of x-ray and neutron powder diffraction patterns.
body:
Software update DBWS. Program for rietveld analysis of x-ray and neutron powder diffraction patterns.
The goal is a new routine for the interpretation of the space group , new profile functions and adjust the code to include a native GUI.
